aw in jurisdictions in which it does business it is my recommendation that a written opinion of Canadian tax counsel be obtained based on a review of the facts and the documents I see this as a sensitive area that requires prudence and if necessary an extra step to make sure that reasonable steps are taken to make sure that Enron policy is observed and complied with Patrick Mackin 
