ember of the board  However I do not feel there would be any material conflicts of interest as Quicksilvers core business is complementary to Enron not competitive with Enron  As a personal matter it is an experience that would be beneficial and would provide valuable personal visibility in our industry I am scheduled to meet with Glen and others at Quicksilver later this month to further discuss this possibility  Would each of you please let me know after due consideration whether you have any objection to or concern with the position  Please do not hesitate to call me x67713 if you have any questions or wish to discuss this further Thanks Jim Hughes 
